bilingual.source: In a way, this failure is beneficial.
bilingual.target: 从某种程度上说，这次失败是有益的。

bilingual.source: Drinking water is beneficial for your health.
bilingual.target: 喝水对你的健康是有益的。

bilingual.source: Many spiders are beneficial because they eat insects.
bilingual.target: 许多蜘蛛是有益的，因为它们吃昆虫。

bilingual.source: A gene mutation can sometimes bring beneficial changes.
bilingual.target: 基因突变有时会带来有益的变化。

bilingual.source: The bacteria in yogurt are harmless and even beneficial.
bilingual.target: 酸奶中的细菌是无害的，甚至是有益的。

bilingual.source: A balanced diet is beneficial for your overall well-being.
bilingual.target: 均衡饮食对你的整体健康是有益的。

bilingual.source: A random mutation can sometimes lead to a beneficial trait.
bilingual.target: 随机突变有时会导致有益的特征。

bilingual.source: Many fruits and vegetables contain beneficial phytochemical.
bilingual.target: 许多水果和蔬菜都含有有益的植物化学物质。

bilingual.source: The notion that stress can be beneficial is counterintuitive.
bilingual.target: 压力有益的观念是违反直觉的。

bilingual.source: Meditation can be beneficial for reducing stress and anxiety.
bilingual.target: 冥想对减轻压力和焦虑是有益的。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: It can be inferred that the "high-income threshold" in Australia is <highlight>beneficial</highlight> to business owners.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 可以推断，澳大利亚的“高收入门槛”对企业主有利。

examination_example.sentence: The researchers calculated that the stress-reducing effects of hugging explained about 32 percent of that <highlight>beneficial</highlight> effect.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 研究人员估算，拥抱的减压效果能够解释这一有益影响的32%。

examination_example.sentence: However, Cortina said, early exposure is <highlight>beneficial</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但科尔蒂纳说，早期接触是有益的。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: favorable or advantageous; resulting in good

examination_example.sentence: But there is a whole range of other health issues that turning up the radio could be <highlight>beneficial</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是还有一系列其他的健康问题，打开收音机可能是有益的。

examination_example.sentence: However, for the same reason, music can be very <highlight>beneficial</highlight> if one is in pain.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，出于同样的原因，如果一个人处于痛苦之中，音乐会非常有益。

examination_example.sentence: While the sun's rays can age and harm our skin, they also give is <highlight>beneficial</highlight> Vitamin D.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 虽然太阳光会老化并伤害我们的皮肤，但它们也会给我们提供有益的维生素D。
